    "ResultsThe review included 15 observational studies and 3 RCTs and synthesised evidence from different medical fields and populations.",
    "Chatbots systematically collect information through targeted queries and data retrieval, improving patient engagement and satisfaction.",
    "The results show that chatbots have great potential for history taking and that the efficiency and accessibility of the healthcare system can be improved by 24/7 automated data collection.",
    "Bias assessments revealed mixed methodological quality.",
    "Among the 16 observational studies, 6 (37.5%) had a high quality."
